Sentencas: A high-performance thin film solid oxide fuel cell (TF-SOFC) was fabricated using a scandia-stabilized zirconia (ScSZ) thin film electrolyte deposited on an anodized aluminum oxide supporting structure.
Titulo: High-performance thin film solid oxide fuel cells with scandia-stabilized zirconia (ScSZ) thin film electrolyte

Sentencas: The crystallinity and ionic conductivity were evaluated of the ScSZ film that was deposited by sputtering at room temperature.
Titulo: High-performance thin film solid oxide fuel cells with scandia-stabilized zirconia (ScSZ) thin film electrolyte

Sentencas: No phase transformation of ScSZ film was observed during heating to the TF-SOFC operation temperature of 500 degrees C.
Titulo: High-performance thin film solid oxide fuel cells with scandia-stabilized zirconia (ScSZ) thin film electrolyte

Sentencas: The oxygen ion conductivity of the ScSZ film was determined to be 0.00024 S/cm at 500 degrees C on polycrystalline Al2O3.
Titulo: High-performance thin film solid oxide fuel cells with scandia-stabilized zirconia (ScSZ) thin film electrolyte

Sentencas: The maximum power density of the TF-SOFC including the 280 nm thick ScSZ thin film electrolyte was measured to be 227 mW/cm(2) at 500 degrees
Titulo: High-performance thin film solid oxide fuel cells with scandia-stabilized zirconia (ScSZ) thin film electrolyte
